      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Here's a roundup of the **latest AI news today** (as of May 3, 2026):\n\n---\n\n### 🤖 AI Industry & Business\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**Google** is committing **$40 billion** to its AI rival **Anthropic**, as the firm looks to secure cloud dominance and fuel the expansion of Gen AI infrastructure."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**Alphabet** is breaking away with a **63% surge in Google Cloud revenue** to **$20 billion** for Q1 2026, amid the ongoing AI infrastructure arms race."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**Amazon** has launched **Amazon Connect Talent** (now available in preview), which uses AI \"teammates\" to conduct **24/7 interviews** and score candidates, easing the hiring process."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n---\n\n### 🧑‍⚖️ Legal & Policy\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "A **civil trial between Elon Musk and Sam Altman** kicked off and could help define the future of artificial intelligence — it is scheduled to run for **four weeks**, with a cast of prominent tech executives set to take the stand."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Musk claimed Altman **betrayed the original principles of OpenAI** to remain a nonprofit and that the company benefited from his money and connections."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**Google** joins **OpenAI** in allowing the **Pentagon** to use its AI systems, as rival Anthropic remains embroiled in a court battle after seeking stronger safeguards."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n---\n\n### 💻 AI Models & Technology\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The AI industry is releasing new models at an **unprecedented rate**, with capabilities that seemed cutting-edge months ago now being baseline expectations."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Key trends include **reasoning models** (like OpenAI o1 and DeepSeek-R1) trading speed for accuracy, **multimodal capabilities** becoming standard across frontier models, and efficiency improvements delivering GPT-4-level performance at dramatically lower costs."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n---\n\n### 🔬 AI Research (MIT)\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "A **new dataset** of **30,000+ competition math problems** from 47 countries gives AI researchers a harder test — and students worldwide a better training ground."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "A **new training method** improves the reliability of AI confidence estimates without sacrificing performance, addressing a root cause of **hallucination** in reasoning models."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Building on a long-standing MIT–IBM collaboration, a **new lab** will chart the convergence of **AI, algorithms, and quantum computing**."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n---\n\n### 📈 Finance & Infrastructure\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**AI chipmaker Cerebras** is said to be targeting up to **$4 billion in an IPO**."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n- "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**Meta** has acquired a **robotics AI company** to help build humanoid technology."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n---\n\nFor more in-depth coverage, check out sources like [TechCrunch AI](https://techcrunch.com/category/artificial-intelligence/), [MIT News](https://news.mit.edu/topic/artificial-intelligence2), [Bloomberg AI](https://www.bloomberg.com/ai), and [AI Magazine](https://aimagazine.com/)."
